<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Amicbridge ‚Äì A Trusted Network for Lending & Borrowing</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Amicbridge connects verified people who want to lend and borrow money through a trusted, private network.">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --bg-light: #111827;
      --card: #020617;
      --accent: #2563eb;
      --accent-soft: rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
      --text: #e5e7eb;
      --muted: #9ca3af;
      --border: #1f2937;
      --danger: #dc2626;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      --radius-lg: 18px;
      --radius-xl: 26px;
      --max-width: 1120px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1e293b 0, #020617 45%, #000 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.5;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .shell {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,23,42,0.96), rgba(15,23,42,0.8), transparent);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.9);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1rem 0;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 0, #60a5fa 0, #2563eb 40%, #1d4ed8 65%, #1e293b 100%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(37,99,235,0.65);
    }

    .logo span {
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.75rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .nav-links a {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 0.1rem;
    }

    .nav-links a::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -0.15rem;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #60a5fa, #2563eb);
      transition: width 0.18s ease-out;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .nav-cta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .btn {
      appearance: none;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      padding: 0.55rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      transition: all 0.18s ease-out;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-outline {
      border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.7);
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.4);
    }

    .btn-outline:hover {
      border-color: #e5e7eb;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.9);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #4f46e5);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(37,99,235,0.7);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(37,99,235,0.9);
      filter: brightness(1.05);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.95);
      border: 1px solid rgba(51,65,85,0.9);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: #60a5fa;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(15,23,42,0.8);
    }

    main {
      flex: 1;
    }

    /* Hero */

    .hero {
      padding: 3.25rem 0 3.5rem;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.25fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-kicker {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: #93c5fd;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 3.2vw + 1.2rem, 3.3rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      font-weight: 720;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-title span {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #60a5fa, #a855f7, #ec4899);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 34rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.7rem;
    }

    .hero-cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.9rem;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .hero-note {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
    }

    .pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-top: 0.8rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
    }

    .pill {
      padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(55,65,81,0.9);
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.7);
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .hero-card {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(37,99,235,0.25), transparent 48%),
                  radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(236,72,153,0.3), transparent 52%),
                  var(--bg-light);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      padding: 1.2rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(51,65,85,0.9);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(148,163,184,0.09), transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .card-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .card-badge {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: #a5b4fc;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(129,140,248,0.8);
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.8);
    }

    .match-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }

    .match-col {
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.88);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 0.7rem 0.75rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(31,41,55,0.9);
    }

    .match-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .match-name {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.1rem;
    }

    .match-meta {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .match-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.25rem;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(22,163,74,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.7);
      color: #bbf7d0;
      margin-top: 0.35rem;
    }

    .match-chip.danger {
      background: rgba(220,38,38,0.15);
      border-color: rgba(248,113,113,0.9);
      color: #fecaca;
    }

    .risk-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
    }

    .risk-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .risk-meter {
      flex: 1;
      margin-left: 0.8rem;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(31,41,55,0.9);
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .risk-fill {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e 0, #eab308 50%, #ef4444 100%);
      transform-origin: left;
      transform: scaleX(0.42);
    }

    .trust-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-top: 0.7rem;
    }

    .trust-dots {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.2rem;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(148,163,184,0.6);
    }

    .dot.active {
      background: #60a5fa;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(37,99,235,0.28);
    }

    /* Sections */

    section {
      padding: 2.5rem 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.9);
    }

    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
      max-width: 34rem;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .section-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .steps-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .step {
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.9);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(31,41,55,0.9);
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .step-num {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(37,99,235,0.18);
      border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.9);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #bfdbfe;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .step-title {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .step-text {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.9);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 1.2rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(31,41,55,0.9);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .bullet-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .bullet-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .bullet-list li::before {
      content: "‚Ä¢";
      color: #60a5fa;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      margin-top: 0.1rem;
    }

    .pill-strip {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }

    .pill-soft {
      padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(37,99,235,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.4);
      color: #bfdbfe;
    }

    .pricing-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .price-card {
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.95);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(55,65,81,0.9);
      padding: 1.2rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .price-card.highlight {
      border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.9);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 55px rgba(37,99,235,0.6);
    }

    .price-tag {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 650;
      margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    }

    .price-tag span {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .badge-small {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: #a5b4fc;
      padding: 0.22rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(129,140,248,0.7);
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.9);
    }

    .price-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0.7rem 0 1rem;
      padding: 0;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .price-list li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .price-list li::before {
      content: "‚úì";
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #4ade80;
      margin-top: 0.12rem;
    }

    .faq-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.87rem;
    }

    .faq-item {
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(31,41,55,0.9);
    }

    .faq-q {
      font-weight: 550;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .faq-a {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.9);
      padding: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-links a {
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .steps-grid,
      .two-col,
      .pricing-grid,
      .faq-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0,1fr);
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 2.5rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-cta-row {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .hero-card {
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
  <header>
    <div class="shell nav">
      <div class="logo">
        <div class="logo-icon">AB</div>
        <span>Amicbridge</span>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#how">How it works</a>
        <a href="#safety">Safety</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="nav-cta">
        <button class="btn btn-outline">Log in</button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary">Apply to join</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="shell hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="hero-kicker">A private network for money you trust</div>
          <h1 class="hero-title">
            Be the bridge between people who <span>lend</span> and people who <span>borrow</span>.
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            Amicbridge connects verified members who want to lend and borrow money in a structured, transparent way.
            We are not a bank ‚Äî we are the network between people and capital, with clear rules and digital contracts.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-cta-row">
            <button class="btn btn-primary">Request to borrow</button>
            <button class="btn btn-secondary">Apply as a lender</button>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-note">
            <span>üîí</span>
            <span>Identity verified, contracts signed digitally, payments tracked inside the platform.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pill-row">
            <div class="pill">Private network access</div>
            <div class="pill">No public listings</div>
            <div class="pill">Transparent terms</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <div class="card-header">
              <div class="card-title">Example match in Amicbridge</div>
              <div class="card-badge">Live network</div>
            </div>
            <div class="match-grid">
              <div class="match-col">
                <div class="match-label">Borrower</div>
                <div class="match-name">Sara ‚Ä¢ Member since 2024</div>
                <div class="match-meta">NOK 80 000 ‚Ä¢ 24 months</div>
                <div class="match-chip danger">High commitment ‚Ä¢ Signed contract</div>
              </div>
              <div class="match-col">
                <div class="match-label">Lender</div>
                <div class="match-name">Henrik ‚Ä¢ Verified lender</div>
                <div class="match-meta">Expected return 7.2% p.a.</div>
                <div class="match-chip">Diversified ‚Ä¢ 14 active loans</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="risk-row">
              <div class="risk-label">Risk / reward profile</div>
              <div class="risk-meter">
                <div class="risk-fill"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-bar">
              <span>All activity is logged and visible to both sides.</span>
              <div class="trust-dots">
                <div class="dot active"></div>
                <div class="dot active"></div>
                <div class="dot"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section id="how">
      <div class="shell">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div class="section-label">How it works</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">A structured process between people, not chaos between strangers.</h2>
          <p class="section-text">
            Amicbridge is a curated network. Every member is verified, every agreement is documented, and every payment flow is transparent.
            Here‚Äôs what happens when you join.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="steps-grid">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div class="step-title">Join and verify</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              Create an account, confirm your identity, and tell us whether you want to lend, borrow, or both.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div class="step-title">Set your preferences</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              Define how much you want to borrow or lend, time horizon, and your tolerance for risk.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div class="step-title">We match inside the network</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              Based on your profile, we suggest matches with other members. You always see terms up front.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">4</div>
            <div class="step-title">Sign and track</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              Agreements are signed digitally, payments are monitored, and you can track everything in one dashboard.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Safety -->
    <section id="safety">
      <div class="shell two-col">
        <div>
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-label">Safety & trust</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Trust is the real currency. We treat it like capital.</h2>
            <p class="section-text">
              Amicbridge is designed for people who take money seriously. We combine identity checks, structured agreements,
              and transparent data so everyone understands what they are agreeing to.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>What we do for safety</h3>
            <ul class="bullet-list">
              <li>Verify the identity of all members before they join the network.</li>
              <li>Require written, digital agreements for every loan relationship.</li>
              <li>Use secure, encrypted connections for all communication and data.</li>
              <li>Provide clear documentation of terms, payment schedules, and obligations.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="pill-strip">
              <div class="pill-soft">Identity verification</div>
              <div class="pill-soft">Digital agreements</div>
              <div class="pill-soft">Secure data</div>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top:0.7rem;font-size:0.8rem;color:#6b7280;">
              Amicbridge is a matchmaking network, not a bank. We do not guarantee returns or repayment. Members must always
              assess their own risk and, where necessary, seek independent legal and financial advice.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Why members trust Amicbridge</h3>
          <p>
            Our members are willing to pay to access the network because it reduces the chaos and guesswork that usually comes
